      "description": "CFD-predicted NIH compared against in vitro measurement at elevated speed, reduced flow. Predicted NIH = 0.0072 g/100L; measured NIH = 0.0068 ± 0.0007 g/100L. Relative error 5.9%. Uncertainty in wall shear stress distribution and exposure time integration is acknowledged in the narrative; the Monte Carlo ensemble for this condition was folded into the global sensitivity report.",
